    "MissionTokens": {
        "Contractor|BountyTitleSuper": [
            "A Troublesome Task",
            "An Extremely Difficult Task",
            "An Onerous Task"
        ],
        "Contractor|BountyDescriptionSuper": [
            "I fear this is another one of those assignments that will take your full skillset to see to completion.\n\n[TargetName] is aboard a very heavily armed vessel protected by at least two equally armed escorts. They are traveling near [Location|Address].\n\nNot for the faint of heart.\n\nFondly,\nVaughn",
            "If you hadn't already proven yourself time and again, I would say that this next kill would most definitely cement my esteem of your abilities.\n\nAboard a heavily defended and well escorted ship traveling near [Location|Address] is one [TargetName]. Please kill them.\n\nFondly Yours,\nVaughn",
            "Powerful people make powerful enemies as is evident in this next assignment. \n\nDespite [TargetName]'s well-appointed vessel and extremely qualified escort ships, it is up to you to see them dead. You should be able to find them near [Location|Address].\n\nYou have my full faith.\n\nFondly,\nVaughn"
        ],
        "Contractor": [
            "Vaughn"
        ],
        "Danger": [
            "Make sure to bring your full arsenal when you go hunting. Since [TargetName|Last] usually captains a bigger multicrew ship and springs the extra credits for escort, something tells me you might need the extra firepower."
        ],
        "Location|Address": [
